{"tid":2100964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【水費飆升】多區居民指6月水費貴一倍　水務署稱疫情間估算讀數","createTime":"2020-07-09T12:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T03:23:32.000Z","uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"889965a314b422bfdacbfc9480370348cc7259e5","tid":2100964,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"近日多區的區議員接獲居民反映，指6月的水費單金額飆升，有居民懷疑是水務署抄錶出錯。《香港01》到訪兩區屋邨，不少居民承認6月的水費賬單貴了一倍，但未知原因為何。有區議員表示，向水務署了解事件後，得悉是2月疫情嚴峻時沒有派員上門抄錶，按估算計算水費，以致有住戶的實際用水量被低估，故6月份的水費單會補回差額，呼籲居民若有疑問，可主動與水務署聯絡。水務署表示，由本年1月至5月，該署收到約6,000宗各類型的水費查詢，包括水錶損壞、內部供水系統漏水、估算水錶讀數等，較去年同期多出2,000多宗。<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/38F3Ur2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38F3Ur2&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=6a754eb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38F3Ur2</a>"},{"pid":"b1dab61b3b089734e14a6b02068923800e570fe9","tid":2100964,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8eb03aafadcbd7da6b01b3defe016b9f052352d","tid":2100964,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"斷鳩估 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1293586d4002c1be4a5f152b447201677430e736","tid":2100964,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee713ed408bd7778239a454df2a0cf14bcbb7aa","tid":2100964,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，睇返上年差唔多時間張單都無咁貴"},{"pid":"8f5c35c376fee595ba73fc1fefe982e45ea0ca64","tid":2100964,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"被水費"}]}